Class JsonArray

java.lang.Object
io.micronaut.json.tree.JsonNode
io.micronaut.json.tree.JsonArray
@Internal public class JsonArray extends JsonNode
Public to allow special handling for conversion service. Use JsonNode.isArray() to distinguish nodes.
Since:
3.1
